1. Count Total Records
Command:
db.purchases.countDocuments()

2. Find Total Sales Amount
Aggregation Command:
db.purchases.aggregate([
  {
    $group: {
      _id: null,
      totalSales: { $sum: "$price" }
    }
  }
])

3. Total Sales by Category
Aggregation Command:
db.purchases.aggregate([
  {
    $group: {
      _id: "$category",
      totalAmount: { $sum: "$price" }
    }
  }
])

4. Purchase Count by Location
Aggregation Command:
db.purchases.aggregate([
  {
    $group: {
      _id: "$location",
      totalPurchases: { $sum: 1 }
    }
  }
])

5. List All Purchases Above â‚¹80
Filter Command:
{ "price": { $gt: 80 } }
